<description>&lt;section class=&quot;&quot; data-tools=&quot;135&amp;#x7F16;&amp;#x8F91;&amp;#x5668;&quot; data-id=&quot;91525&quot; data-mpa-powered-by=&quot;yiban.io&quot;&gt;&lt;section&gt;&lt;section&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-ratio=&quot;1&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/RiacFDBX14xDq5EjfNPfeeHGZe7ghDuoQIiadibQFbPekdd9t6KtzSKgLABYFpLwgjX1py2TxnHg4MknKsCWfhzzw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;600&quot; data-width=&quot;100%&quot; width=&quot;75.5781px&quot;/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section&gt;&lt;section&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;北美留学生日报&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section&gt;&lt;span&gt;每天优质海外新闻 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section&gt;&lt;span&gt;百万留学生都在关注&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section&gt;&lt;section&gt;&lt;section https:=&quot;&quot; no-repeat=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-ratio=&quot;1.3574074074074074&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/RiacFDBX14xDq5EjfNPfeeHGZe7ghDuoQrIt8cQz7COYOl7thm3vBRnqm8XB6yAx9qtZzwrtwVJlJ2VAkbw5m8w/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;1080&quot; title=&quot;&amp;#x53D4;&amp;#x53D4;.jpg&quot; width=&quot;auto&quot;/&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.5547368421052632&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/RiacFDBX14xCHPSpZiaKpsg99yXb9RGPz1A43ZGqmpwKWLAiaOKdBO6t3YHzsGT1SfghvJaaWDqpXtGGYMSG9jKfw/640?wx_fmt=png&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;950&quot; width=&quot;558px&quot;/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section data-role=&quot;outer&quot; label=&quot;Powered by 135editor.com&quot;/&gt;&lt;section class=&quot;&quot;/&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-backh=&quot;436&quot; data-backw=&quot;558&quot; data-before-oversubscription-url=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/RiacFDBX14xBJkCOJ3ibPn34UgPePZjYvsI1VhnckUHdsvBGic0yFztwaCgzlJWYgJNhOhrdlkg8C22E6BudsWTGg/?wx_fmt=png&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.7808988764044944&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/RiacFDBX14xBJkCOJ3ibPn34UgPePZjYvsI1VhnckUHdsvBGic0yFztwaCgzlJWYgJNhOhrdlkg8C22E6BudsWTGg/640?wx_fmt=png&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;712&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;本文授权转载自雅思中国网，公众号ID：ieltsim&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;事情是这样的，有网友发了一条微博引来无数人留言：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-backh=&quot;154&quot; data-backw=&quot;526&quot; data-before-oversubscription-url=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/IzH1ZaLJwKkNXYwXFib676ib3ibEHEMG16zDohjYZrMGRWQXMbT8JzDPvgfiaGImJF9fEzFVnXKFyT5mCRa7Wic7eicA/?wx_fmt=png&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.29244444444444445&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/IzH1ZaLJwKkNXYwXFib676ib3ibEHEMG16zDohjYZrMGRWQXMbT8JzDPvgfiaGImJF9fEzFVnXKFyT5mCRa7Wic7eicA/640?wx_fmt=png&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;1125&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;汉语真是博大精深，一个字都可以有好几个读音，不同读音的同一个字连在一起，都能组成一句通顺无比的语句。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;这样的句子，怕是要汉语十级才能看懂，真是难为外国人了！&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-backh=&quot;144&quot; data-backw=&quot;526&quot; data-before-oversubscription-url=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/IzH1ZaLJwKkNXYwXFib676ib3ibEHEMG16z0jFoDISylota0LJCD2CzaYNVIv6Eq37pFU4fcfibIzBxibaiaiahUyyPAg/?wx_fmt=png&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.2737777777777778&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/IzH1ZaLJwKkNXYwXFib676ib3ibEHEMG16z0jFoDISylota0LJCD2CzaYNVIv6Eq37pFU4fcfibIzBxibaiaiahUyyPAg/640?wx_fmt=png&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;1125&quot; width=&quot;auto&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;这时候孙俪估计要对邓超说：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ins class=&quot;adsbygoogle&quot; data-ad-layout=&quot;in-article&quot; data-ad-format=&quot;fluid&quot; data-ad-client=&quot;ca-pub-1837452791782084&quot; data-ad-slot=&quot;7041996284&quot;/&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;我也想花花花花花过的钱&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;记住：花过的钱不能再花了！&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-backh=&quot;141&quot; data-backw=&quot;526&quot; data-before-oversubscription-url=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/IzH1ZaLJwKkNXYwXFib676ib3ibEHEMG16zT6H1eibpPoHcBsCe7Sw4qkFfN2ukx0EMIqaey6FVzIGpJIW4hDozCBg/?wx_fmt=png&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.26844444444444443&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/IzH1ZaLJwKkNXYwXFib676ib3ibEHEMG16zT6H1eibpPoHcBsCe7Sw4qkFfN2ukx0EMIqaey6FVzIGpJIW4hDozCBg/640?wx_fmt=png&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;1125&quot; width=&quot;auto&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;俏俏说：我就要跳跳跳跳过过儿过过的格子！&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;请自行断句&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-backh=&quot;110&quot; data-backw=&quot;524&quot; data-before-oversubscription-url=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/IzH1ZaLJwKkNXYwXFib676ib3ibEHEMG16z8Vsku6yExeIJIKHI8wuN4bnF1gsg0qGZJI7837ibZhdqlmHHDUkDVoQ/?wx_fmt=png&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.21066666666666667&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/IzH1ZaLJwKkNXYwXFib676ib3ibEHEMG16z8Vsku6yExeIJIKHI8wuN4bnF1gsg0qGZJI7837ibZhdqlmHHDUkDVoQ/640?wx_fmt=png&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;1125&quot; width=&quot;622px&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;请问这句话是天天和你说的吗？&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;天天说这天天天天气不好&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;越看越像夭。。。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-backh=&quot;175&quot; data-backw=&quot;526&quot; data-before-oversubscription-url=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/IzH1ZaLJwKkNXYwXFib676ib3ibEHEMG16zyhO2ClumknPOK0MP31OL1eNLTg5nxicQOlz4FcPGzl88etYdGMTEggA/?wx_fmt=png&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.33244444444444443&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/IzH1ZaLJwKkNXYwXFib676ib3ibEHEMG16zyhO2ClumknPOK0MP31OL1eNLTg5nxicQOlz4FcPGzl88etYdGMTEggA/640?wx_fmt=png&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;1125&quot; width=&quot;auto&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;然后他们就一起过上了没羞没臊的生活？&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;咳咳。。。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;请注意言辞&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

